{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"addNotificationCenterDelegate:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)UNUserNotificationCenterDelegate","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"id<UNUserNotificationCenterDelegate>"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"delegate","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"delegate","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The delegate object that conforms to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UNUserNotificationCenterDelegate"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. Must not be nil."}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use this method to register your own "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UNUserNotificationCenterDelegate"},{"type":"text","text":" alongside Pushwoosh’s built-in delegate."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Pushwoosh uses a delegate proxy to forward notification center callbacks to all registered delegates,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"enabling multiple components to respond to notification events without conflicts."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This is the recommended way to handle notification center events when using Pushwoosh SDK 7.0+,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as it avoids conflicts with Pushwoosh’s own notification handling."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Typical use cases:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Integrating multiple push notification SDKs"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Adding custom notification handling logic (e.g., analytics, local notifications)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Implementing custom notification actions","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Examples","anchor":"Examples","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Register AppDelegate as a notification delegate:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["func application(_ application: UIApplication,","                 didFinishLaunchingWithOptions launchOptions: [UIApplication.LaunchOptionsKey: Any]?) -> Bool {","    Pushwoosh.configure.addNotificationCenterDelegate(self)","    return true","}"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Register a dedicated notification handler:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class NotificationHandler: NSObject, UNUserNotificationCenterDelegate {","","    func userNotificationCenter(_ center: UNUserNotificationCenter,","                                willPresent notification: UNNotification,","                                withCompletionHandler completionHandler: @escaping (UNNotificationPresentationOptions) -> Void) {","        if !PWMessage.isPushwooshMessage(notification.request.content.userInfo) {","            completionHandler([.banner, .sound])","        }","    }","","    func userNotificationCenter(_ center: UNUserNotificationCenter,","                                didReceive response: UNNotificationResponse,","                                withCompletionHandler completionHandler: @escaping () -> Void) {","        if !PWMessage.isPushwooshMessage(response.notification.request.content.userInfo) {","            \/\/ Handle your custom notification","            completionHandler()","        }","    }","}","","let handler = NotificationHandler()","Pushwoosh.configure.addNotificationCenterDelegate(handler)"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Objective-C:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"objc","code":["[Pushwoosh.configure addNotificationCenterDelegate:self];"],"type":"codeListing"},{"name":"Note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Use ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWMessage\/isPushwooshMessage:"},{"type":"text","text":" to distinguish Pushwoosh notifications from your own and handle only non-Pushwoosh notifications in your custom delegate."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","style":"note"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PushwooshConfig"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PushwooshConfig\/addNotificationCenterDelegate:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Adds a custom ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UNUserNotificationCenterDelegate"},{"text":" to the Pushwoosh notification center delegate proxy.","type":"text"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pushwooshconfig\/addnotificationcenterdelegate:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Method","title":"addNotificationCenterDelegate:","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"addNotificationCenterDelegate:"}],"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(cs)PushwooshConfig(cm)addNotificationCenterDelegate:","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addNotificationCenterDelegate:"}]},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWMessage/isPushwooshMessage:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWMessage\/isPushwooshMessage:","kind":"symbol"